Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.72,0:00:07.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,久违的陆地啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.62,0:00:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚踏实地的感觉真爽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然热血的我还是最适合这广袤的大地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的热血也只能持续到下个港口为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能否改走陆路前往雷之国呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:26.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,估计没戏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.14,0:00:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在身处水之国的境内
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由大大小小的岛屿组成的水之国
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.63,0:00:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同雷之国并未接壤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然…一想到要乘船就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那离雷之国还有多远
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概还有四分之一的路程
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.66,0:00:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 在港口听闻附近有山寨出没
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.19,0:01:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么山寨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.14,0:01:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无怨无仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:14.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此相遇就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.78,0:01:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留下买路财吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.81,0:01:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:23.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个护额是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.39,0:01:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是来自木叶以身弑晓的漩涡鸣人大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 山寨就是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:51.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.37,0:01:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一模一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.75,0:02:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里像了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们无视我 还在吐槽吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:07.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是木叶的漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我算个啥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你连自己是谁都不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥你们也带着木叶的护额呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.21,0:02:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才是真正的漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吹牛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,货真价实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过没想到竟然山寨鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来名气十足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.66,0:02:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.18,0:02:37.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.73,0:02:40.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能摆平他的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的…决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此一决胜负 看看谁才是真正的鸣人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.89,0:02:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少莫名其妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:54.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 努力战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.99,0:02:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输了的话他就是真货咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是没辙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴倒是嚣张得很
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.93,0:05:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这连热身运动都算不上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这东西我们没收了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么处置这个男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在赶路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.52,0:05:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种家伙 暴打一顿扔路边就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样合适吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.97,0:05:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他逃掉再制造麻烦的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.57,0:05:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可就声名狼藉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.64,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.88,0:05:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.25,0:05:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我负责追踪这名盗贼 名叫伊己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢和这家伙对峙的屈指可数
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.28,0:05:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看也就我俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙可是让人闻风丧胆的大盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙才不是漩涡鸣人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥你会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:06:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了…我才是正品漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 你是真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是 我的大名竟然被盗贼所用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.07,0:06:06.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太混蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你在追踪这盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是官府人士吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后就拜托这位大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧上路
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过大哥…你没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来可没有那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.77,0:06:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不可貌相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是忍者大师伊已大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来您这么牛逼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不能以貌取人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.65,0:06:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.13,0:06:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了 哥们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是被干掉了怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,废物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.24,0:07:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想干掉他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.62,0:07:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是真正的漩涡鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到会在这里遇到真货
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳 你的借口我不想听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来计划好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干掉身为盗贼的你 从而提升我的名望
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.02,0:07:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在即将打响的战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有名望可无法展现自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果干掉漩涡鸣人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能大名远扬了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.11,0:07:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…这么危险的事打住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.68,0:07:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对你的恩惠你都忘了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果没有我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还在一个人孤独地哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.18,0:07:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:08:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己是我唯一的伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过下次要找我们能干掉的做对手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫我们能干掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.80,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我动真格的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管它是一个还是两个漩涡鸣人 都不在话下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.12,0:08:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我吧 伊己
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.12,0:08:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了就好 能明白的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人在这附近当山贼是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经有数人遇险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.80,0:08:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据说是个大红脸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但为何鸣人会在这里做山贼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:48.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙不是拯救了村子的英雄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细情况还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有传言说漩涡鸣人在村里是个麻烦的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许成为叛忍了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果叛离村子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶应当也在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.70,0:09:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他再转卖给木叶 一定能有个好价钱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是没问题吗 对方可是漩涡鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.53,0:09:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说漩涡鸣人连中忍考试都没通过
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕那英雄传说也是捏造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.56,0:09:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.96,0:09:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对于身为佣兵忍者的我们而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是财源吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我拿出真本领
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本没必要做这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一来 看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了社会 为了人民
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保卫世界和平的伟大忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己大爷就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己真帅
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.32,0:09:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己如果动真格的 一定很了不起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定能在战场上鹤立鸡群
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.41,0:09:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要做农活 我要当英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 戴上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来你又是漩涡鸣人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 邦纳…不是 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.06,0:10:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有猎物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.67,0:10:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅行商人你该不会输了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无怨无仇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.34,0:10:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此相遇就是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我漩涡鸣人留下买路财吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是正是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老实放下的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.39,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那些家伙不是旅行商人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你会自动送上门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.56,0:11:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.29,0:11:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.43,0:11:25.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.89,0:11:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙才不是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是个废物盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这家伙的外貌符合消息所述
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:36.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还带有木叶的护额
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.00,0:11:40.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这家伙的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.80,0:11:44.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敢来捣乱的话 连你一起收拾了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没那回…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.73,0:11:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对…我是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙才不是我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深山老林里出来的农二代
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:59.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愿干农活 以为自己是忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整天想抓我出名 死缠不休
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山寨忍者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我滚一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然连你一起收拾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.77,0:12:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办…该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.33,0:12:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子终于不闹腾了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧赶路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.11,0:12:47.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:48.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.49,0:12:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.01,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:12:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们交给我的盗贼被其他的盗贼给劫走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:09.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想请你们替我夺回那个盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是忍者大师来着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.45,0:13:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己动手不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个…现在…我有点…不在状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忍者还要看什么状态吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.45,0:13:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我们有急事必须走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,况且你是官府中人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回衙门找人帮忙不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.76,0:13:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.77,0:13:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是盗贼抢走盗贼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也就是窝里反而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙虽然是个坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.85,0:13:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也并非穷凶极恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.80,0:13:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙因为外表凶悍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直被大家讨厌 欺负
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去就一直很胆小 很善良
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.36,0:14:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,善于照顾他人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.77,0:14:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当了解那家伙嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是官府中人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.59,0:14:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始就让人觉得很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 我老实坦白所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.52,0:14:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是所有的经过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.32,0:14:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为啥做这种蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.98,0:14:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 帮帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是拯救了木叶的英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.07,0:14:41.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然他是同伴 为什么让他做这些事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然他是同伴 为什么不替他想想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.64,0:14:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.59,0:14:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.84,0:14:53.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他才不是什么同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.69,0:14:58.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是图个方便才不会理他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.81,0:15:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是什么同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.43,0:15:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然说不是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言 那家伙算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:21.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许你一直把他当笨蛋耍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.02,0:15:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那家伙从小就和你在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.10,0:15:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一同走到现在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.98,0:15:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还不算同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:36.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.38,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有时间确实可以听听你的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我们不能轻易暴露身份和所在地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:16:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你忘记见到过我们的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.37,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 拜托了 我一个人办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.13,0:16:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:12.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱莫能助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.38,0:16:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.03,0:16:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己做决定
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.03,0:16:29.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙…是同伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.64,0:16:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起爆符
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.11,0:16:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是这家伙的同伴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是同伴 也不是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.36,0:17:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.37,0:17:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.29,0:17:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.87,0:17:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.16,0:17:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个没用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.43,0:17:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不救你的话 我们的计划可就搁浅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.33,0:17:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:46.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在利用你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.47,0:17:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像个鬼一样被大家厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有伊己愿意和我做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:18:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时 我也被其他人欺负啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们说只要我整你 就不会再欺负我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊己跟我成为了挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让你逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.25,0:18:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他们看看我们最后的志气
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.49,0:18:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管到哪里 我都会跟着伊己的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么点本事还想赢我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.48,0:18:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活捉漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.77,0:18:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个不用留活口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能像漩涡鸣人那样厉害就能保护伊己了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:48.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.24,0:18:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.56,0:18:57.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你把我当成你的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邦纳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.38,0:19:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 你们两个 看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时仅凭你的只言片语无法让人信服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就试探了你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.34,0:19:23.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试探我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.62,0:19:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在非常感动
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.38,0:19:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有弃朋友于不顾 信任朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位大爷 你们以为是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位传说中的大人物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是保护了木叶的英雄 漩涡鸣人大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:46.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给力点 你可是鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.02,0:19:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.46,0:19:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是天下的英雄 漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漩涡鸣人 一生一次的大暴动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把漩涡鸣人的名字还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这名号我可伤不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.46,0:20:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.94,0:20:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们接下来想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为忍者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.58,0:20:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会经历如此恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.45,0:20:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来不太适合我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回故乡去过平凡的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能和伊己一起 去哪儿都行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.33,0:20:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.19,0:20:56.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们两个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大的声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:02.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐地活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.27,0:21:06.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挚友真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.99,0:21:11.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们总有一天会像他们一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砂隐上忍 手鞠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.61,0:22:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受我的挑战吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:22:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:22:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吾名为猿飞木叶丸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代火影之孙
